practitioner.about:
Dr. Gelan Mohamed Sadek is a part of the General Medicine department at Medcare. She has qualified as a Member, Royal College of Physicians (MRCP), UK, and has completed her MBBCh from Ain Shams University in Egypt.

Dr. Sadek has worked at the Dr. Yousri Jouher Hospital in Egypt, the Abdulla Kamal Private Medical Clinic in Bahrain and at the Al Khawaneej Health Center, Dubai Health Authority.

Dr. Sadek helps patients with treatments related to diabetes management, preventive medicine and smoking cessation advice, hypertension, urinary tract infection management and more.

Dr. Sadek’s hobby is reading and she speaks Arabic and English.
